verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Stutinthun stutinthun naa kaalochana
Karthayagu devuni raatrivelalo naa
Antharindriyamu naaku nerpun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Naadu swaastya paaneeya bhaagamu naa Yehovaa
Neeve kaapaadedavu manohara stalamulalo
Paalu kalgenu stutinthun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Shresta maino swaastyamu naaku kalgenu sadaa
Kaalamu Yehovaa yandu naa; gurini nilpu chunnaanu
Gana nenu stutin tun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Naa kudi paarshya mandaayana yunnaadu gaana
Kadalchabada lenu ennadu; andu che naa hrudaya
Maanandinchunu Stutintun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Naa shareeramu surakshithamabugaa nivasinchu
Chunnadi elananagaa nee parishudduni kullu
Pattaniyaavu Stutintun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Jeevamu gala nee maargamunu neevu naakila
Theliya jesedavu neeve naa kshemmaa dhaaramani
Ninnu Stutintun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Sarvonnathudaa nee sannidhilo
Sampooma santosha mentho galadu nee kudi
Chethilo nitya sukhamulu galavu Stutintun{/lang-eng}
